Class Report

java.lang.Object
entity.Report
All Implemented Interfaces:
ReportDetails
public class Report extends Object implements ReportDetails
The Report class represents a system-generated analytical report containing filters, raw data entries, and a timestamp. Interface implemented: - ReportDetails This class is part of the Entity layer in the BTO Management System.
